{"tid":1207750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[代po請廣傳]有關明天13/6塞鐵不合作運動","createTime":"2019-06-12T07:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T07:53:17.000Z","uid":104256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89785c40ad5d5757565896361ab1e214ecf070d5","tid":1207750,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"塞鐵方向包括三點<br />\n1: 堵塞地鐵主要幹道<br />\n2: 保障支援路線不受阻 (荃灣線全線 或 太子/旺角至炮台山)<br />\n3: 引導更多市民支援堵塞地鐵<br />\n<br />\n方向不一者, 請勿加入新群組. 事在必行.<br />\n如方案有漏洞, 有問題, 透過大家討論, 獲得&rdquo;完善方案&rdquo;<br />\n呼籲唔塞者, 一律踢出新群組<br />\n<br />\n新群組TELEGRAM:<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/saveHK613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FsaveHK613&d=Upau0OFRhNBgg6kYd6CVy51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=4b5d8cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/saveHK613</a><br />\n<br />\n另外, 各線路ADMIN希望大家呼籲各線路人員加入大群, 如有意繼續協助組織塞地鐵，請與ADMIN聯絡， 以免舊有線路ADMIN本身就係鬼, 一獲熟。<br />\n<br />\n邀請各 &ldquo;行動組&rdquo; &ldquo;勇武派&rdquo; 協助成為&rdquo;塞鐵行動組領頭&rdquo;<br />\n有意者私CHAT所有新大GROUP ADMIN<br />\n<br />\n有任何覺得&quot;非常重要意見&quot; 請私CHAT ADMIN<br />\n&quot;蘑菇菇&quot; &quot;HKWorker&quot; &quot;TinkyChan&quot; &quot;Doeadeer&quot;<br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，於Facebook，Whatsapp，各大塞鐵Group，論壇<br />\n此次行動為極速版(明天執行，無人就唔成事，太耐就俾警察有所準備)"},{"pid":"3cee786a330e5396c2bffbe4abd248d917a3b05f","tid":1207750,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"aa69294e782922ee3bf266c9d724a043bfc1f463","tid":1207750,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3fac4cb44b2d0ef8f9374cd8e17ef1db6db7b980","tid":1207750,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"psih"},{"pid":"435450ab778c65c7b5964f8a2a56ccbdb29e4d43","tid":1207750,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fcbcdd2265d6b012801dd52a0